SUMMARY:2026 Wooden Shoe Tulip Festival
DESCRIPTION:Mark your calendars! The 2026 Wooden Shoe Tulip Festival is tentatively scheduled for March 20 – April 26. Date specific tickets available in early March. Enjoy 40 acres of 100 varieties of tulips and on 4 acres at Wooden Shoe Gardens. \nThe Tulip Festival is packed with activities for the whole family. From hot air balloons\, a children’s play area\, and endless photo opportunities\, wine tastings\, and their specialty gift shop to our food & craft market\, there’s so much to do in their beautiful setting! \nAll tickets must be purchased online in advance—secure your spot and enjoy a seamless entry to the Wooden Shoe Tulip Festival! \nTickets are available online only to minimize crowds and allow for the best guest experience. \nThe festival is open: \n\nMonday – Thursday: 9 am – 6 pm\nFriday: 9 am – 7 pm\nSaturday: 8 am – 7 pm\nSunday: 8 am – 6 pm\n\nChildren 12 and under may enter the festival free when accompanied by a ticketed adult. 
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/2026-wooden-shoe-tulip-festival/2026-03-24/
LOCATION:Wooden Shoe Tulip Festival
CATEGORIES:Active,Family Fun,Farm,Kids Calendar,Outdoor,Plants & Nature
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://pdxparent.com/wp-content/uploads/wooden-shoe-tulip-farm.jpg
END:VEVENT
