DESCRIPTION:Indoor Play Parks are officially back! 🎉 Cozy up in the Conestoga Recreation Center! Families with children up to 6 years of age can gather to interact and develop motor and social skills during Indoor Play Park. Adult supervision is required; only youth drop-in fees apply. ***Before you go – check THPRD’s website  – activity calendar for facility closures throughout the season. \n\nConestoga Recreation Center: Mondays/Wednesday/Friday/Sunday 9:30-11:30\n$8 out of district\, $5.75 cedar hills/free for adults\n\n 
